  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators plan to perform a prospective observational cohort study of patients
      undergoing MPFL reconstruction for the treatment of episodic patellar instability in the
      absence of significant degenerative disease. The investigators will follow these study
      subjects for a minimum of two years to monitor their functional and clinical outcome.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
